by gharlan at 2016-05-11T20:10:06Z

fixed tests and harmonized comment handling around `{`.
Please take a look at changed test cases.

input:
```php
if (true) // foo
{
    bar();
}

function () // foo
{
};
```

expected before this pr:
```php
if (true) {
    // foo

    bar();
}

function () {// foo
};
```

harmonized result after merging this pr:
```php
if (true) { // foo
    bar();
}

function () { // foo
};
```

